OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly dry
OL,6,Fthrough this evening and overnight,
OL,7,Fthough often rather cloudy. Some light
OL,8,Frain or drizzle possible at times,
OL,9,Fmainly over the hills. With the added
OL,10,Fbreeze, temperatures will be on the
OL,11,Fmild side.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FMostly dry, with some bright
OL,14,For sunny spells spells. Thicker cloud
OL,15,Fmoving in from the west later in the
OL,16,Fday, with spells of rain possible.
OL,17,FMild with lighter winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
