OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FGenerally dry through this period as
OL,7,Fhigh pressure builds in. Feeling
OL,8,Fpleasant in the sunny spells by day,
OL,9,Fbut fresh by night where skies remain
OL,10,Fclear. Some fog patches too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
